::English::

Language: English, Russian, French, Spanish
Platform: Windows XP | Vista | Seven / Mac OS X 10.4 | 10.5 | 10.6
Developer: canon.com 

The disc comes with cameras Canon. Contains software for viewing, editing, organizing and printing images, as well as control the camera.

Contents of the disk:

 Digital Photo Professional v3.9.1.0:

DPP is designed to convert the RAW-files from digital cameras, Canon, this version supports all SLR cameras and almost all of "Soap," the company Canon, released today. DPP supported file formats: CR2, CRW, TIFF / TIF, JPEG, JPEG / JFIF. Options settings RAW-file: white balance, brightness (exposure), contrast, dynamic range, recipes, "*. vrd", batch processing retouch RAW / JPEG / TIFF: cropping (cropping, image rotation), a stamp, tone curve, color, saturation, brightness, contrast curve Tone, retouching, etc. ..


 ZoomBrowser EX v6.6.0.23:

The tool provides import, organize, print and export images.


 EOS Utility v2.9.0.0:

Utility management functions of the camera via a computer. Designed for copying images from the camera to the computer to determine the settings on the camera, for photographing with simultaneous recording on the computer.


 PhotoStich v3.1.22.46:

Application for the "glue" panoramas. Allows you to mount a "vertical" and horizontal "panoramas from multiple images.


 Original Data Security Tools v1.9.0.1:

Application for verification of original data, decryption, as well as a driver for Original Data Security Kit OSK-E3 (optional).
